The paper focuses on graph database systems, which are primarily used for storing and processing large, complex datasets. This falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses data organization techniques and query execution, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
